BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260422T063000
DTEND:20260422T075400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.669ft at 06:30\n-0.065ft at 07:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Decent mix of WNW/NW swells and some S swell also showing. Knee-waist high
  surf for average zones\, pushing chest-shoulder high for select spots abl
 e to pull in the S swell on tap.\n\nAnother drained low tide to try and wo
 rk around\, but winds look pretty light all day (and much better than Tues
 day's S wind). The afternoon stays in play with mellow SW/WSW wind wrappin
 g into town.
END:VEVENT
