BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260423T063000
DTEND:20260423T091200
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.995ft at 06:30\n-0.065ft at 09:12\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Mix of WNW/NW swells and some S swell is slightly down from Wednesday\, bu
 t a new mid-period WNW may be on the rise through the back half of the day
 . This could push better spots back into the chest to shoulder high range 
 in the afternoon. \n\nConditions are looking much better compared to previ
 ous days with light AM winds currently expected. 
END:VEVENT
